{"type":null,"faqId":47138,"title":"荣耀小K配对时收到验证码为乱码？","answer":"<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">\n<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" id=\"softwareDescription\" jQuery17105265378906306457=\"16\">\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">绑定配对时，扫描二维码之后，需要输入手表号码进行验证，请按照以下步骤操作：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 确认扫描二维码之后输入的是手表SIM卡号，而不是管理员手机卡号。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果是自己手机收到的乱码，那么输入的就是手机的卡号而不是手表的。需要核实，输入手表的卡号。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 确认手表版本，若手表软件版本为1.35.4.X以下版本，请用户通过花粉论坛指导帖一键升级至1.35.4.X版本后再进行配对。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">一键升级指导链接：http://cn.club.vmall.com/thread-6620036-1-1.html</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a jQuery17105265378906306457=\"22\" href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/820ca_lepkc.jpg\"><img width=\"400\" height=\"565\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/820ca_lepkc.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a jQuery17105265378906306457=\"23\" href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/820cb_tisa6.jpg\"><img width=\"400\" height=\"404\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/820cb_tisa6.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a jQuery17105265378906306457=\"24\" href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/820cc_139il.jpg\"><img width=\"400\" height=\"361\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/820cc_139il.jpg\"></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2658","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444979293000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":23,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"K1-G01,荣耀小K,儿童手表,K1,绑定,配对,连接,验证码,乱码","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}